{"tid":1252962,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱有個死老坑同我爭關愛座坐畀我一拳打到瞓撚低","createTime":"2019-06-23T10:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T00:19:38.000Z","uid":254923,"like":59,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8d9733d8e47db97951ccefd1938a9703721984b5","tid":1252962,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:00:30.000Z","msg":"啱啱收工搭坐地鐵 <br />\n咁做撚左成日野就就想搵個位坐下瞌陣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知畀我係茫茫人海嘅車廂入面搵到個位 我就唔理三七廿一坐撚左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係我好快瞌著左之後無啦啦有人拍撚醒左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我呢世人最撚憎人係我瞓覺嗰陣搞撚醒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（係中學試過打到個叫醒我嘅阿sir入廠）<br />\n心諗邊個咁撚戇鳩整醒我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抬頭一望係個老野黎 要我讓位畀佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我一黎就屌撚柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：個老野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：後生仔啊⋯<br />\n我一野閘撚住佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：後你老母 屌你老母啊死老嘢整撚醒我係咪要我幫你送殯啊<br />\n佢聽到我咁撚惡一時間都反應唔切<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我都係想你讓個位畀老人家抖下姐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：屌你老母我畀你抖邊撚個畀我抖啊？又唔見我老細畀我抖？我朝朝返九點都已經好撚攰 你仲要整撚醒我 <br />\n我講左兩句d火氣都黎料 個老而不見情況唔對路想閃人 可惜已經太遲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：死老坑想走？<br />\n我講完之後就一拳打落佢心口到 佢個人即刻彈高2米 跟住就攤左係到 周圍d人都呆撚哂 <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我真係好撚唔鍾意人整醒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2ae1e35cb85e3d03f4a5ea03a97c6bf56ab3ef","tid":1252962,"uid":240518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:01:57.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"c82836106f191c8df2f572585d66b2505214b03f","tid":1252962,"uid":9769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:03:16.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"e6d4339304e8c527c1b6fce6c7d7892b8de724f1","tid":1252962,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:03:36.000Z","msg":"認同請正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2830d6379fb75cd97425938fb48e8210eb6f6fea","tid":1252962,"uid":187889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:04:13.000Z","msg":"thanks for sharing"},{"pid":"230b8774b18fbd0af0e3bcc0235d42dc2dd5df0b","tid":1252962,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c82836106f191c8df2f572585d66b2505214b03f","tid":1252962,"uid":9769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:03:16.000Z","msg":"1/10"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:07:39.000Z","msg":"真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f3431a66d5294795f73d267e78cf6de7771b59d","tid":1252962,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6a2ae1e35cb85e3d03f4a5ea03a97c6bf56ab3ef","tid":1252962,"uid":240518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:01:57.000Z","msg":"Ok"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:07:52.000Z","msg":"Ya<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c48ac0792584ab872447126f791dfe5f7c7ec10b","tid":1252962,"uid":183576,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:09:54.000Z","msg":"好型，想含<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b405515f2408df30a5f00c3a9fafbd03998b77f2","tid":1252962,"uid":254923,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c48ac0792584ab872447126f791dfe5f7c7ec10b","tid":1252962,"uid":183576,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:09:54.000Z","msg":"好型，想含<img src